crawler
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:1. a slow sheep that has missed a first muster 2. an aged ewe or wether with footrot.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:straggler
